title: 10 pugs who celebrated National Pug Day a little too hard
text: Comment By More Content Now staff Posted Oct. 15, 2015 @ 3:22 pm We’re all about enjoying photos of pugs pretty much every day of the year, but today isn’t just any regular day… It’s Pugtober 15th, or National Pug Day , and our celebrations have NOTHING on the partying these pugs are doing. And after so much revelry, it’s inevitable these pugs need to take a nap, like these 10 cute little pups. (Navigate slideshow through arrows above.)
